title: Edgar Winter Group 1974 DKRC
description:

EDGAR WINTER GROUP DKRC 1974 VHS RIP
Likely August 1974
Broadcast Nov 30 1974
Taped from a Canal Jimmy rerun in the 1990s

Edgar Winter-kbds,sax,vocals
Rick Derringer-guitar,vocals
Dan Hartman-bass
Chuck Ruff-drums

Free Ride
Easy Street
Teenage Love Affair
River's rising
Extended jam
Rock'n'Roll Hoochie Koo
Free Ride + credits


Lineage: trade vhs gen unknown/standalone dvd burner
NTSC
34 m 27 s 

Canal Jimmy logo on top right throughout.

A decent if not so crisp copy
